| Cast                    = * {{WP|Benedict Cumberbatch}} as [[Stephen Strange (Earth-199999)|Doctor Strange / Dr. Stephen Strange]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/10/benedict-cumberbatch-doctor-strange-movie-cast-862815/|title=Benedict Cumberbatch To Play Doctor Strange|last=Fleming|first=Mike, Jr.|work=Deadline|date=27 October 2014|accessdate=28 October 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://marvel.com/news/movies/23754/benedict_cumberbatch_to_play_doctor_strange|title=Benedict Cumberbatch to Play Doctor Strange|last=Strom|first=Marc|work=Marvel.com|date=4 December 2014|accessdate=4 December 2014}}</ref>
** Cumberbatch also provides the facial motion capture for [[Dormammu (Earth-199999)|Dormammmu]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2016/10/25/benedict-cumberbatch-plays-a-second-marvel-character-in-doctor-strange|title=Benedict Cumberbatch Plays a Second Marvel Character in Doctor Strange|last=Krupa|first=Daniel|work=IGN|date=25 October 2016|accessdate=26 October 2016}}</ref>

* {{WP|Chiwetel Ejiofor}} as [[Karl Mordo (Earth-199999)|Karl Mordo]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2015/06/chiwetel-ejiofor-doctor-strange-baron-mordo-marvel-benedict-cumberbatch-1201441281/|title=Chiwetel Ejiofor's 'Doctor Strange' Character Revealed: He'll Play Baron Mordo|last=Fleming|first=Mike Jr.|work=Deadline|date=11 June 2015|accessdate=11 June 2015}}</ref>

* {{WP|Rachel McAdams}} as [[Christine Palmer (Earth-199999)|Christine Palmer]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thewrap.com/rachel-mcadams-to-star-in-marvels-doctor-strange/|title=Rachel McAdams to Star in Marvel's 'Doctor Strange'|author=Sneider, Jeff and Linda Ge|work=The Wrap|date=14 September 2015|accessdate=14 September 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MLE17hoQZr4|title=DOCTOR STRANGE Comic Con 2016 - Benedict Cumberbatch, Tilda Swinton, Rachel McAdams, Mads Mikkelsen|author=Flicks And The City|work=Youtube|date=23 July 2016|accessdate=23 July 2016}}</ref>
